      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### ClickHouse \u2014 OTel logs+traces SQL &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; RFC-0019 Phase B\nLong-retention (**TTL 90d**) OLAP over OpenTelemetry logs+traces \u2014 the cross-day SQL the 7-day, LogsQL/TraceQL-only ops primaries can't give, plus the `otel_logs`\u2194`otel_traces` **`trace_id` JOIN** in one store. **Logs-first**: `otel_logs` (100%, unsampled) counts; `otel_traces` (head-sampled) are exemplars. Metrics stay on VictoriaMetrics \u2014 never here."
      },
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Overview \u2014 health at a glance",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Span rate",
      "description": "Avg spans/sec over the range (all services).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
        "uid": "${ds}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
            "uid": "${ds}"
          },
          "editorType": "sql",
          "rawSql": "SELECT $__timeInterval(Timestamp) AS time, count()/60.0 AS v FROM otel.otel_traces WHERE $__timeFilter(Timestamp) AND ServiceName IN (${service:singlequote}) GROUP BY time ORDER BY time",
          "format": 1,
          "queryType": "timeseries",
          "pluginVersion": "4.19.0"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "blue",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "mean"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "wideLayout": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error rate",
      "description": "Percent of Server spans with StatusCode=ERROR. Yellow \u22651%, red \u22655%.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
        "uid": "${ds}"
